cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SY

The paper presents a novel non-parametric density estimation approach using a neural network, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method is also applicable to computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY) where density estimation is a common task. The paper mentions the use of stochastic optimization, which is a common technique in neural networks and falls under the category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
